ney Bewes]] (Acting Diploma 1956) *[[Christopher H. Bidmead]] (Acting Diploma 1962) *[[Isabel Bigley]] (Acting Diploma 1948) *[[Theodore Bikel]] (Acting Diploma 1948) *[[Leo Bill]] (Acting Diploma 2001) *[[Pepper Binkley]] (BA Acting 2004) *[[Norman Bird]] (Acting Diploma 1943) *[[Nora Francisca Blackburne]] (Acting Diploma 1936) *[[Adam Blackwood (actor)|Adam Blackwood]] (Acting Diploma 1981) *[[Isla Blair]] (Acting Diploma 1963) *[[Michael Blakemore]] (Acting Diploma 1952) *[[Caroline Blakiston]] (Acting Diploma 1957) *[[JB Blanc]] (Acting Diploma 1990) *[[Joyce Bland]] (Acting Diploma 1927) *[[Peter Blythe]] (Acting Diploma 1958) *[[Ross Boatman]] (Acting Diploma 1986) *[[Ken Bones]] (Acting Diploma 1973) *[[Oliver Boot]] (Acting Diploma 2001) *[[James Booth]] (Acting Diploma 1956) *[[Annika Boras]] (BA Acting 2005) *[[Bruce Bould]] (Acting Diploma 1969) *[[Peter Bowles]] (Acting Diploma 1956) *[[David Bradley (English actor)|David Bradley]] (Acting Diploma 1968) *[[Booker Bradshaw]] (Acting Diploma 1964) *[[Hilda Braid]] (Acting Diploma 1948) *[[Gina Bramhill]] (BA Acting 2009) *[[Kenneth Branagh]] (Acting Diploma 1981) *[[Bernard Bresslaw]] (Acting Diploma 1953) *[[Alan Bridges]] (Acting Diploma 1948) *[[Anita Briem]] (BA Acting 2004) *[[Richard Briers]] (Acting Diploma 1956) *[[Francine Brody]] (Acting Diploma 1983) *[[Faith Brook]] (Acting Diploma 1942) *[[Sian Brooke]] (BA Acting 2002) *[[Jacqueline Brookes]] (Acting Diploma 1953) *[[Arthur Brough]] (Acting) *Brett Brown (BA Acting 2009)<ref>{{cite web |title=Brett Brown — RADA |url=https://www.rada.ac.uk/profiles/brett-brown/ |website=www.rada.ac.uk |language=en-gb}}</ref> *[[Pamela Brown (actress)|Pamela Brown]] (Acting Diploma 1936) *[[Angela Browne]] (Acting Diploma 1955) *[[Tom Browne (broadcaster)|Tom Browne]] (Acting) *[[Dugald Bruce Lockhart]] (Acting Diploma 1994) *[[Joshua Bryant]] (Acting Diploma 1964) *[[Andrew Buchan]] (BA Acting 2005) *[[Jessie Buckley]] (BA Acting 2013) *[[Kate Buffery]] (Acti